'''JK-13''' was a [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatist]] [[JK-13 security droid]] that was captured by the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]]. During testing, it was able to defeat a [[Droideka/Legends|droideka]] and [[Advanced Recon Commando/Legends|ARC trooper]] [[Sirty]], although it was defeated by [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Kit Fisto/Legends|Kit Fisto]].<ref name="TCSWE">{{CSWECite|II|167|JK-13}}</ref>

